# Voedzame Shakes - Cursor AI Context

## Figma Design
Design source: https://www.figma.com/make/pdxQrgt2kBCruayxbJp6oI/Nutritious-Shakes-App-Design

Use this Figma design as the visual reference for all styling work.

## Tech Stack
- Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS (NO frameworks, NO React)
- Static JSON for recipes
- localStorage for persistence  
- Service Worker for offline PWA

## Key Files
- `index.html` - Single page with 3 views
- `js/app.js` - All logic
- `css/style.css` - All styling
- `recipes.json` - Recipe data
- `sw.js` - Service Worker

## Design Rules
- Mobile-first, accessibility-focused
- Large fonts (18px+ base) for older users
- Protein displayed before calories
- No prep time on cards
